dc_title_s: Rainfall Totals, greater Green Bay, WI area 2004
dc_description_s: This data represents rainfall totals for the greater Green Bay, WI area in the year 2004 (from 05/11 to 08/27) at various time intervals.[Rainfall patterns for large storm events within 230 kilometers of the Green Bay, WI Next-Generation Radar (NEXRAD) station (KGRB). The files are Storm Total Precipitation (NTP) for 2003 to 2014 and Storm Total Accumulation (PTA) for 2015 to 2017 downloaded from the NEXRAD Inventory at the NOAA National Climatic Data Center and visualized through the Fox-Wolf Hydrologic Dashboard.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
